          "severity": "2-3 organ failure (MODERATE)",
          "criteria": "SOFA 2-3 points in 2-3 systems",
          "treatment": "ICU. Treat underlying cause (source control, antibiotics). Organ-specific support: lung-protective ventilation, fluid resuscitation, vasopressors, RRT if AKI. Nutrition. Glucose control."
